==開發==
[[File:Elliot_Page,_2010_(cropped).jpg|thumb]]

《超能殺機：兩個靈魂》在2012年E3上由Quantic Dream執行長David Cage在索尼發表會上第一次釋出預告影片，本遊戲開發耗時三年，劇本根據艾略特·佩吉的說法長達兩千頁<ref>{{cite web|url=http://herocomplex.latimes.com/2012/07/19/ellen-page-beyond-game/|title=Ellen Page is ‘Beyond’ real in ‘emotional and subversive’ game|last=Pham|first=Alex|publisher=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|date=2012-07-19|accessdate=2012-08-29|archive-date=2012-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018063722/http://herocomplex.latimes.com/2012/07/19/ellen-page-beyond-game/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在開發期間原本的作曲家[[Normand_Corbeil|Normand Corbeil]]在2013年1月25日過世<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.joystiq.com/2013/01/28/heavy-rain-composer-normand-corbeil-passes-away-aged-56/|title=Heavy Rain Composer Normand Corbeil Passes Away, Age 56|publisher=Joystiq|date=2013-01-28|accessdate=2013-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130202022243/http://www.joystiq.com/2013/01/28/heavy-rain-composer-normand-corbeil-passes-away-aged-56/|archive-date=2013-02-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，遊戲配樂由[[Lorne_Balfe|Lorne Balfe]]接手<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hans-zimmer.com/index.php?rub=news_3&id_news=862 |title=Lorne Balfe to score the video game BEYOND - TWO SOULS |publisher=Hans-Zimmer.com |date=2013-04-14 |accessdate=2013-06-25 |archive-date=2015-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150208225726/http://www.hans-zimmer.com/index.php?rub=news_3&id_news=862 |dead-url=no }}</ref>並在2013年八月長期與Balfe合作的[[漢斯·季默|漢斯·季默]]加入了製作團隊當中<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.joystiq.com/2013/08/22/beyond-two-souls-soundtrack-from-hans-zimmer-and-lorne-balfe/|title=Beyond: Two Souls soundtrack from Hans Zimmer and Lorne Balfe|last=Conditt|first=Jessica|publisher=Joystiq|date=2013-08-22|accessdate=2013-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130822113134/http://www.joystiq.com/2013/08/22/beyond-two-souls-soundtrack-from-hans-zimmer-and-lorne-balfe/|archive-date=2013-08-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

在2013年4月27日《超能殺機：兩個靈魂》在翠貝卡影展上發表了35分鐘的遊戲畫面，艾略特·佩吉和威廉·達佛皆有出席，此遊戲是史上第二款在影展中出現的遊戲<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.destructoid.com/beyond-two-souls-tribeca-trailer-35-minutes-of-footage-252645.phtml |title=Beyond: Two Souls Tribeca trailer + 35 minutes of footage |publisher=Destructoid |last=Pinsof |first=Allistair |date=2013-04-28 |accessdate=2013-06-25 |archive-date=2013-07-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130703101239/http://www.destructoid.com/beyond-two-souls-tribeca-trailer-35-minutes-of-footage-252645.phtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

